Package kaitech.api.model

Interface Menu

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MenuImpl, MenuTblImpl.DbMenu
    public interface Menu
    This interface implements Menus. A business may have multiple menus such as a normal menu and a vegetarian menu. The main purpose of Menu is to collect a list of MenuItems that belong together to assist in organisation.
